{"tid":431134,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"發現人類先係地球最恐怖嘅野","createTime":"2017-10-10T12:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T21:29:05.000Z","uid":135891,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1b0658f35d24645f8011ebcc7ad0d01aae85ca81","tid":431134,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T12:03:28.000Z","msg":"最近諗住寫個故講世界末日，所以就揾下有咩大災難可以世界末日<br />\n地震？多極都係十幾廿萬<br />\n海嘯？04年南亞海嘯都係卅萬 所有沿海地區浸一次都未必有一億<br />\n疾病？以前科技差仲有死幾千萬人嘅黑死病 近代沙士香港七百萬人都係死咗幾百人<br />\n<br />\n死得最多人就只有戰爭 <br />\n二戰已近接近一億人<br />\n核戰更加不敢想像 冚球鏟都仲得<br />\n<br />\n所以真係人類先最可能搞到世界末日"},{"pid":"1f50d82e3ba978ba72fd9518fc402c0c37c0138c","tid":431134,"uid":151833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T14:12:48.000Z","msg":"你依家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd872a7d64394b3422d1f0db987c0c6423888cb","tid":431134,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T21:08:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你依家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3525faa347eed7e6b97da5d18f1e960ab9687686","tid":431134,"uid":63843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T21:29:05.000Z","msg":"套套災難片背後既訊息都係講人類先係罪魁禍首"}]}